<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?><song><lyrics>[V1]
 1. Ka umna lei In hi mang mahleh,
 Khuta sak loh kumsawt In ka nei;
 Zie In chu ngaiin ka galdawt ka tung thei puoi,
 Ka taksa sietlei In hin ei nang.

[V2]
 Gam ka nei gam lopi,
 Hukdampa'n kei dinga A bawlsa;
 Sietlei ah kumsawt chenna ding mun ka nei puoi,
 Gam hawih zaw diek vana tih loh chu.

[V3]
 2. Ka umna lei ka mauna gam hi,
 Aw, bangtikleh ka pawt san ta dem ?
 Lungsietna Lal pakcha'n Amah chawian dingin,
 Ka taksa sietlei In hin ei nang;.

[V4]
 3. Muonna leh chawlhdamna ka hawla,
 Zie leisiet chung ahin a um puoi;
 Ginna'n gam thiengtho ka galdawt ka tung thei puoi,
 Ka taksa sietlei In hin ei nang,

[V5]
 4. Abraham mah bangin tuhin chu,
 Ginnan gamtiem lam chu ka zuon hi;
 Mi thiengthote le gam nuom chu chang chiet dingin,
 Ka taksa sietlei In hin ei nang.</lyrics>
<title>Kumsawt In Ka Nei</title>
<hymn_number>293</hymn_number>
</song>